          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What to Expect from Your First Cleaning</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">A complete guide to getting started with professional cleaning.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

